OL,3,CBank of Scotland branch set to close
OL,4,Cits doors
OL,6,FKelso's Bank of Scotland branch is set
OL,7,Fto close, the area's MP has revealed.
OL,9,FMP for Berwickshire, Roxburgh and
OL,10,FSelkirk John Lamont said in a post on
OL,11,FX that the bank had notified him of
OL,12,Fthe decision, which he described as
OL,13,F"just not acceptable" and "the wrong
OL,14,Fdecision".
OL,16,FThe Kelso branch will close its doors
OL,17,Ffor the final time on June 18, 2026.
OL,19,FThe Conservative MP continued: "Banks
OL,20,Fhave abandoned our communities in the
OL,21,FBorders.
