OL,3,CBank of Scotland branch set to close
OL,4,Cits doors
OL,6,F"This is the latest in a series of
OL,7,Fclosures. Not everyone wants to, or
OL,8,Fcan, use online banking."
OL,10,FThe politician's post comes after a
OL,11,Fseries of bank closures in the
OL,12,FBorders, including in Hawick and
OL,13,FMoffat, the latter of which prompted
OL,14,Fquestions from the area's MSP in the
OL,15,FScottish Parliament.
OL,17,FIn his post, Mr Lamont said he has
OL,18,Fbeen told by the Bank of Scotland that
OL,19,Fit will provide a 'community banker'
OL,20,Fin place of the branch.
