OL,3,CBank of Scotland branch set to close
OL,4,Cits doors
OL,6,FThe Bank of Scotland says that this
OL,7,Fcommunity banker will "provide face to
OL,8,Fface services to customers including
OL,9,Fmaking payments, account enquiries and
OL,10,Fonline banking support."
OL,12,FThe MP said that he would ask "what
OL,13,Flevel of service this will provide to
OL,14,Flocal people".
OL,16,FA Bank of Scotland spokesperson said:
OL,17,F"Customers want the freedom to bank in
OL,18,Fthe way that works for them and we
OL,19,Foffer more choice and ways to manage
OL,20,Fmoney than ever before.
