OL,3,CBank of Scotland branch set to close
OL,4,Cits doors
OL,6,F"In addition to our app, customers can
OL,7,Fuse the Post Office or visit our local
OL,8,FCommunity Banker in Kelso. Customers
OL,9,Fcan also walk into any Bank of
OL,10,FScotland and deposit cash at PayPoint
OL,11,Flocations.
OL,13,F"We're giving our customers the
OL,14,Fflexibility to bank wherever and
OL,15,Fwhenever they need us."
